FROM patients
WHERE gender = 'M'

FROM patients

SELECT first_name
FROM patients

SELECT first_name,last_name
FROM patients

UPDATE patients
SET allergies = 'NKA' 
WHERE allergies IS NULL

SELECT concat(first_name,' ',last_name)
from patients

SELECT first_name,last_name,province_name
FROM patients INNER JOIN province_names ON patients.province_id = province_names.province_id

SELECT COUNT(patient_id)
FROM patients
WHERE year(birth_date)=2010

SELECT first_name,last_name,height
FROM patients
order by height DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT * FROM patients
WHERE patient_id IN (1,45,534,879,1000)

SELECT COUNT(patient_id)
FROM admissions

SELECT * FROM admissions
WHERE admission_date = discharge_date

SELECT patient_id, COUNT(patient_id)
FROM admissions
WHERE patient_id = 579

SELECT distinct city
FROM patients
WHERE province_id = 'NS'

SELECT first_name,last_name,birth_date
FROM patients
WHERE height > 160 AND weight > 70

SELECT first_name,last_name,allergies
FROM patients
WHERe allergies IS NOT NULL AND city='Hamilton'

SELECT distinct YEAR(birth_date) as yearbirt
FROM patients
order by yearbirt ASC

SELECT distinct first_name
FROM patients
GROUP BY first_name

SELECT patients.patient_id,first_name,last_name
FROM patients INNER JOIN admissions ON patients.patient_id = admissions.patient_id
WHERE diagnosis = 'Dementia'

SELECT COUNT(gender='M') as males, COUNT(gender='F') as females
FROM patients

SELECT first_name, last_name, allergies
FROM patients 
WHERE allergies IN ('Penicillin','Morphine')
ORDER BY allergies asc, first_name, last_name

SELECT patient_id, diagnosis
FROM admissions
GROUP BY diagnosis
having COUNT(*) >= 2

SELECT city, COUNT(patient_id) as numberino
FROM patients
GROUP BY city
ORDER BY numberino DESC, city ASC

SELECT first_name, last_name
FROM patients

SELECT allergies, count(*) as numberino
FROM patients
WHERE allergies IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY allergies
ORDER BY numberino DESC

SELECT first_name, last_name, birth_date
FROM patients
WHERE YEAR(birth_date) between 1970 AND 1979
order by birth_date ASC

SELECT concat(UPPER(last_name),',',LOWER(first_name))
FROM patients
ORDER BY first_name DESC

SELECT province_id, SUM(height) as sumerino
FROM patients
GROUP BY province_id
WHERE sumerino >= 7000;

SELECT MAX(weight)-MIN(weight) as difference
FROM patients

WHERE last_name = 'Maroni'

SELECT day(admission_date) as days, COUNT(*) as admission_count
FROM admissions
group by days
ORDER BY admission_count DESC

SELECT *
FROM admissions
WHERE patient_id = 542
ORDER BY admission_date DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT patient_id, attending_doctor_id, diagnosis
FROM admissions
WHERE (patient_id%2=1 AND attending_doctor_id IN (1,5,19)) OR (attending_doctor_id LIKE '%2%' AND LENGTH(patient_id)=3)

SELECT first_name,last_name, COUNT(attending_doctor_id) as number_of_admissions
GROUP BY doctor_id
FROM admissions INNER JOIN doctors ON admissions.attending_doctor_id = doctors.doctor_id

SELECT doctor_id, CONCAT(first_name,' ',last_name) as fullname, MAX(admission_date) as lastdate, MIN(admission_date) as firstdate 
FROM doctors INNER JOIN admissions ON doctors.doctor_id=admissions.attending_doctor_id
GROUP BY doctor_id

SELECT  province_names.province_name , COUNT(patient_id) as patients
FROM patients INNER JOIN province_names ON patients.province_id = province_names.province_id
GROUP BY patients.province_id
ORDER BY patients DESC

FROM admissions INNER JOIN patients ON admissions.patient_id = patients.patient_id
